branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VX2 for air, manifold type is available with resin body. Up to 10 valves can be mounted on the manifold. Three body sizes are available, with orifice diameter from 2 to 7mm. NBR seal is standard and FKM or EPDM is optional. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.23 to 1.08.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Manifold Base for VX21/22/23 series solenoid valves for air. Available with Rc, NPT and G thread port.
&lt;/p&gt;

